Just to repeat one simple solution presented in the thread  https://stat.ethz.ch/pipermail/r-sig-meta-analysis/2024-March/005126.html

There is an undocumented argument beta in rma.mv(). If one set it to 0 (`beta=0`), one can fit the intercept of an intercept-only model to 0.




